      *       U6      FILES AND DTAARA UPDATED SUCCESSFULLY           *
      *     U7/U8     SET ON IF RECORD OR DTAARA NOT FOUND            *
      *       30      RECORD OR DTAARA NOT FOUND                      *
      *                                                               *
