     FTABTB10 UF  E                    DISK
     FSDBANKPDUF  E                    DISK
      *
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  13 RUNDAT
     I                                       11  11 SUC
      *
     C                     MOVEACPY@      BIS@   80
      *
     C                     MOVE '0'       *INU6
     C                     MOVE '0'       *INU7
     C                     MOVE '0'       *INU8
     C                     SETOF                     30
      *
      ** Update TABTB10
     C           1         CHAINTABTB10              30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '0'
      *
     C           SFLG      IFNE 1
     C                     MOVE 1         SFLG
     C                     UPDATTABTB10F
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     U7U8
     C                     GOTO ENDPGM
     C                     END
      *
      ** Update SDBANKPD
     C           1         CHAINSDBANKPD             30
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '0'
      *
     C           BJSUC     IFNE 'Y'
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       BJSUC
     C                     UPDATSDBANKD0
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     U7U8
     C                     GOTO ENDPGM
     C                     END
      *
      ** Update RUNDAT
     C           *NAMVAR   DEFN           RUNDAT
     C           *LOCK     IN   *NAMVAR                30
      *
     C           *IN30     IFEQ '0'
      *
     C           SUC       IFNE 'Y'
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       SUC
     C                     OUT  *NAMVAR
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     U7U8
     C                     GOTO ENDPGM
     C                     END
      *
      ** Files and dtaara updated successfully - set on U6
     C                     SETON                     U6
      *
